  <brief_title>Can Treatment With Bismuth Reduce Toxicity to Chemotherapy and Radiotherapy?</brief_title>
  <acronym>Bismuth-PBH</acronym>
  <official_title>Can Treatment With Bismuth Reduce Toxicity to Chemotherapy and Radiotherapy? A Clinical, Prospective, Randomized, Blinded Examination of Patients Suffering From Hematological Malignancies Treated With Intensive Chemotherapy and/or Radiotherapy.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
